04:40.881 --> 04:42.347
Angie, go to sleep.

04:42.349 --> 04:44.283
Jimmy...

04:44.285 --> 04:47.886
Ah, voice-mail.
Let me try again.

04:55.596 --> 04:57.629
Jimmy! Get the phone!

04:57.631 --> 04:59.665
Angie, didn't I tell you
never to pinch me?

04:59.667 --> 05:01.033
I can't stand it.

05:01.035 --> 05:02.334
Who is it?

05:02.336 --> 05:04.469
Angie, I just picked
up the phone.

05:04.471 --> 05:05.904
How am I gonna know who it is?

05:05.906 --> 05:07.939
I want to know who it is.

05:07.941 --> 05:09.474
Let me find out,

05:09.476 --> 05:10.942
