05:10.944 --> 05:12.911
And then I will tell you.

05:12.913 --> 05:14.813
Hello?

05:14.815 --> 05:16.581
Mr. valenti, sorry to call you

05:16.583 --> 05:18.984
at such an ungodly hour, but...

05:18.986 --> 05:21.386
It's Gerry Gaci from
the Burman Bank.

05:21.388 --> 05:23.021
Yes, Mr. Gaci?

05:23.023 --> 05:25.524
Did I wake you?

05:25.526 --> 05:27.326
No, no, I've been up for hours.

05:27.328 --> 05:29.428
I went jogging, I
played a round of golf

05:29.430 --> 05:30.929
and I'm getting a pedicure.

05:30.931 --> 05:33.332
It's 5:55, what do
you think I'm doing?

05:33.334 --> 05:35.600
Ha ha ha, Mr. valenti,
you have a transfer

05:35.602 --> 05:37.636
of eight million
dollars coming in.

05:37.638 --> 05:39.838
I need you to verify
these funds.

05:39.840 --> 05:42.541
Can my cfo come down and
sign those papers?

05:42.543 --> 05:45.711
I'm sorry, sir, but we
need you, as president,

05:45.713 --> 05:49.014
to verify such a
large transaction.

05:49.016 --> 05:50.649
You can come in
any time the next

05:50.651 --> 05:52.784
six or seven days.
What do you say?

05:52.786 --> 05:55.420
Okay, I'll come down Friday.

05:55.422 --> 05:57.422
Thank you very much.

05:57.424 --> 05:59.057
I look forward to
meeting with you.

05:59.059 --> 06:00.659
Thank you, bye.

06:00.661 --> 06:02.561
It's the bank.

06:02.563 --> 06:04.930
There's this transfer coming

06:04.932 --> 06:08.633
and they want me
to go in and sign.

06:08.635 --> 06:10.102
Right now?

06:10.104 --> 06:12.003
He's a moron, what do you want?

06:12.005 --> 06:13.972
I'm gonna call, uh...

06:13.974 --> 06:17.442
Go to sleep.

06:22.483 --> 06:23.749
Jimmy!

06:23.751 --> 06:25.951
Jimmy, you okay? What's up?

06:25.953 --> 06:27.552
You're sleeping?

06:27.554 --> 06:29.554
Uh, no, I been up for hours.

06:29.556 --> 06:31.390
I betcha you're in
your underwear.

06:31.392 --> 06:33.091
Those ripped up boxer shorts.

06:33.093 --> 06:35.527
You got a camera
in my room, Jimmy?

06:35.529 --> 06:37.529
No, I don't got a
camera in your room.

06:37.531 --> 06:38.663
Listen, Benny...

06:38.665 --> 06:40.832
I want to go back
to bed so shut up

06:40.834 --> 06:42.768
and let me tell you
what I gotta tell you.

06:42.770 --> 06:44.770
The bank called me and
told me that there's a

06:44.772 --> 06:48.840
transfer for about eight
million coming through

06:48.842 --> 06:51.643
and they want me to
go down and sign.

06:51.645 --> 06:53.812
You want me to go in
and do that for you?

06:53.814 --> 06:55.480
No, they told me
I gotta go down

06:55.482 --> 06:58.049
'cause I'm the ceo. New rules.

06:58.051 --> 07:00.886
Yeah, that's the new
justice department stuff

07:00.888 --> 07:02.687
that's going on.

07:02.689 --> 07:05.123
Yeah. Do I got a problem?

07:05.125 --> 07:08.059
No? Everything's good?

07:08.061 --> 07:10.195
Everything's fine,
everything's good.

07:10.197 --> 07:12.197
Okay, go back to bed.

07:12.199 --> 07:13.698
Okay, yeah.

07:13.700 --> 07:16.034
I'm up, but whatever.

07:16.036 --> 07:17.803
Good night.

07:17.805 --> 07:19.571
Okay, good night.

07:19.573 --> 07:21.673
Morning, whatever it is. Bye.

07:25.678 --> 07:27.012
Alright, Mr. Ryan.

07:27.014 --> 07:30.182
This is nothing personal,
but as you're aware

07:30.184 --> 07:35.120
your loan with this
bank for your house

07:35.122 --> 07:38.457
is a demand loan which means

07:38.459 --> 07:42.060
we can demand
payment at any time.

07:42.062 --> 07:45.130
You're aware of this, right?

07:45.132 --> 07:48.066
Now you've always
made your payments,

07:48.068 --> 07:51.870
but you've also always
been delinquent.

07:51.872 --> 07:54.573
I'm sorry, Mr. Ryan.

07:54.575 --> 07:57.642
I don't have a choice but
I have to call your loan.

07:57.644 --> 08:00.812
You have seven days to
pay it or we have to

08:00.814 --> 08:04.716
realize on its security,
that's your house.

08:04.718 --> 08:07.519
- My house?
- Your house.

08:07.521 --> 08:09.120
What are you talking about?

08:09.122 --> 08:12.023
My house is where I live
with my family, sir.

08:12.025 --> 08:14.092
I understand that,
and you have complete

08:14.094 --> 08:16.127
empathy and
understanding from me.

08:16.129 --> 08:17.796
But I work for a bank,

08:17.798 --> 08:20.232
the bank is run by a board.

08:20.234 --> 08:22.133
All I can do is answer to them

08:22.135 --> 08:25.570
and they want their
payments on your house.

08:25.572 --> 08:28.173
If you don't pay, they
will take your house.

08:28.175 --> 08:29.674
It's as simple as that.

08:29.676 --> 08:31.810
It is not personal,
it is not me.

08:31.812 --> 08:33.979
It is my job to inform you.

08:33.981 --> 08:36.982
How can I not
take it personally?

08:36.984 --> 08:39.751
You're talking about
taking my home

08:39.753 --> 08:41.852
where I live with
my wife and kid!

08:41.855 --> 08:43.688
No, I am not taking your home.

08:43.690 --> 08:45.891
What I am doing is
informing you of the fact

08:45.893 --> 08:47.759
that if you don't
make your payments

08:47.761 --> 08:50.729
my bank will
repossess your home.

08:50.731 --> 08:53.832
It's just the way it is,
Mr. Ryan. I am sorry.

08:57.570 --> 09:00.205
Angie...

09:00.207 --> 09:01.706
Jimmy!

09:01.708 --> 09:03.074
What are you doing?

09:03.076 --> 09:04.776
Jimmy, why are you
wearing that?

09:04.778 --> 09:07.178
I picked a suit for you.
I love this suit on you.

09:07.180 --> 09:09.881
Maybe you should wear it
because I'm wearing this.

09:09.883 --> 09:12.050
I'm going to lunch, I'm
gonna be a few hours

09:12.052 --> 09:14.753
and I'm gonna take
the Mercedes, okay?

09:14.755 --> 09:16.221
No, honey, I want
you to stay here.

09:16.223 --> 09:18.590
Stay, we can hang out
like we used to.

09:18.592 --> 09:20.859
Come on, we'll go to lunch.

09:20.861 --> 09:20.859
Angie...

09:20.861 --> 09:24.062
We'll have a nice day,
we'll go shopping.

09:24.064 --> 09:26.131
Angie, I got some stuff
to do, okay, hon?

09:26.133 --> 09:27.866
What stuff do you gotta do?

09:27.868 --> 09:30.101
Angie, I'll be back in a
couple of hours, okay?

09:30.103 --> 09:31.736
Why don't you get some sleep?

09:31.738 --> 09:33.204
You woke me up early enough.

09:33.206 --> 09:34.940
You think I'm gonna
forget that pinch?

09:34.942 --> 09:36.308
You're not going to
kiss me goodbye?

09:36.310 --> 09:38.610
Stupid of me,
what am I thinkin'?

09:41.147 --> 09:43.281
See ya tonight. Okay?

09:43.283 --> 09:45.250
Ciao, Bella.

09:55.095 --> 09:56.661
Mickey...

09:56.663 --> 09:58.063
! Mickey!

09:58.065 --> 09:59.931
Mickey, the baby's been crying.

09:59.933 --> 10:02.033
Could you just get up?

10:02.035 --> 10:03.668
I got it.

10:11.178 --> 10:13.778
Sonny, baby. Daddy's coming.

10:13.780 --> 10:16.214
I'm coming, son.

10:16.216 --> 10:19.084
Hey, how are you, my son?

10:19.086 --> 10:22.187
Can you keep it down?!

10:24.724 --> 10:25.991
Mr. valenti.

10:25.993 --> 10:27.392
Good morning.

10:27.394 --> 10:28.760
Good morning, Richie.

10:28.762 --> 10:30.161
Nice to see you.

10:30.163 --> 10:31.830
The car's out front.

10:31.832 --> 10:33.632
I didn't have time to wash it.

10:33.634 --> 10:35.767
No big deal. We're good.

10:40.172 --> 10:41.906
Have a good day, buddy.

10:41.908 --> 10:43.341
You too.

10:43.343 --> 10:45.677
Thank you. See you tonight.

10:53.253 --> 10:54.753
'Morning, daddy.

10:54.755 --> 10:56.855
Atta boy.

10:56.857 --> 10:59.324
Hey, how does
mommy look at you?

11:18.145 --> 11:19.310
Hello?

11:19.312 --> 11:20.845
Hey.

11:20.847 --> 11:23.415
I'll be there in
about 15 minutes.

11:23.417 --> 11:25.717
A lot of traffic,
I'm cutting through.

11:25.719 --> 11:27.752
I'm coming down
along the water.

11:59.886 --> 12:03.088
Don't go nuts ordering
a bunch of stuff.

12:03.090 --> 12:05.290
I'm not going to eat
heavy for lunch.

12:05.292 --> 12:07.392
I'm taking Angie to
dinner at that new place.

12:07.394 --> 12:10.095
I don't want to eat two
good meals in one day.

12:10.097 --> 12:13.364
Then I gotta run for a
week to lose one pound.

12:13.366 --> 12:16.401
Ha ha, I'm at that stage now.

12:16.403 --> 12:20.238
I'm almost there.
God bless you.

12:31.184 --> 12:32.050
Jimmy!

12:32.052 --> 12:33.218
Jimmy!

12:33.220 --> 12:36.054
Didn't I tell you
guys to order light?

12:46.800 --> 12:49.000
How you doing, buddy?

12:49.002 --> 12:52.971
Good. How much is a
hotdog and drink?

12:52.973 --> 12:54.372
That'll be four bucks.

12:54.374 --> 12:56.141
How much for just a hotdog?

12:56.143 --> 12:57.375
Three bucks.

12:57.377 --> 12:58.977
Gimme a hotdog.

13:25.538 --> 13:27.438
I know you!

13:27.440 --> 13:32.010
Mickey... Mickey Ryan.

13:32.012 --> 13:33.978
From Alfie's bar.

13:46.559 --> 13:48.526
Oh!

13:48.528 --> 13:50.295
Buddy, you okay?

13:50.297 --> 13:52.063
Come on.

13:52.065 --> 13:54.566
Look like you fell down,
you can't get up.

13:54.568 --> 13:56.401
What do you mean by that?

13:56.403 --> 13:58.236
Just what I said.

13:58.238 --> 14:00.138
I didn't mean anything by it.

14:00.140 --> 14:02.240
You okay, bud? You
look like you got the

14:02.242 --> 14:04.008
weight of the world
on your shoulders.

14:04.010 --> 14:05.543
I'm fine. Sorry about the-

14:05.545 --> 14:07.312
you sure you're gonna be okay?

14:07.314 --> 14:09.280
Anything I can do for you?

14:09.282 --> 14:11.082
Good luck, bud.

14:14.286 --> 14:16.287
Hey, you got room for one?

14:16.289 --> 14:18.489
I got room for no
less than one, baby.

14:18.491 --> 14:20.124
Have a good day.

14:30.604 --> 14:31.936
Good morning, Mr. valenti.

14:31.938 --> 14:33.338
Here are your messages.

14:33.340 --> 14:34.305
Thank you.

14:34.307 --> 14:35.907
Richie, what are
you doing here?

14:35.909 --> 14:37.508
I feel bad about
not getting your car

14:37.510 --> 14:39.210
cleaned up. Can I do it now?

14:39.212 --> 14:40.645
Come on, rich.
It's no big deal.

14:40.647 --> 14:42.547
Please, it'll just
take me a few minutes.

14:42.549 --> 14:44.482
Rich, I got a board
meeting upstairs.

14:44.484 --> 14:46.951
If it's not ready my
wife's gonna kill me.

14:46.953 --> 14:48.052
I understand.

14:48.054 --> 14:50.021
- You sure?
- I promise.

14:50.023 --> 14:51.055
Okay, buddy.

14:51.057 --> 14:52.590
So bring it down here, okay?

14:52.592 --> 14:53.625
For sure.

14:53.627 --> 14:55.026
Thanks.

14:55.028 --> 14:57.195
She's already called six times.

14:57.197 --> 14:59.597
Good morning, Mr. valenti.

14:59.599 --> 15:01.232
Good morning.

15:01.234 --> 15:02.500
Coffee, Mr. valenti?

15:02.502 --> 15:04.235
Uh, not really. You know what?

15:04.237 --> 15:06.504
I didn't sleep much last night.

15:06.506 --> 15:08.206
I'll have one of those -

15:08.208 --> 15:09.474
is that yours?

15:09.476 --> 15:11.075
No, I got it for you.

15:11.077 --> 15:12.377
Thanks.

15:12.379 --> 15:14.145
Benny's waiting in the
boardroom for you

15:14.147 --> 15:15.513
right now.

15:15.515 --> 15:18.049
I gotta make sure I'm out
of here in 30 minutes.

15:18.051 --> 15:19.918
My wife's already called
three million times.

15:19.920 --> 15:21.519
Talk about being obsessive.

15:21.521 --> 15:23.421
So I just want to
make it a quick thing.

15:23.423 --> 15:24.656
Is the agenda all ready?

15:24.658 --> 15:26.257
It's all ready for you.

15:26.259 --> 15:27.458
Jimmy, how are you?

15:27.460 --> 15:28.927
Good. Gentlemen, good morning.

15:28.929 --> 15:29.994
'Morning.

15:29.996 --> 15:31.329
So you got everything
on the bank?

15:31.331 --> 15:32.463
I do.

15:32.465 --> 15:33.932
Thanks Benny.

15:35.579 --> 15:36.068
Hang on.

15:36.069 --> 15:40.038
Let's sit down and we'll
get everything organized.

15:45.577 --> 15:48.079
Okay, so, explain to
me, if you don't mind,

15:48.081 --> 15:49.580
why we're going down there

15:49.582 --> 15:51.316
to verify this on Friday.

15:51.318 --> 15:52.583
Well, basically,

15:52.585 --> 15:54.218
a customer sends
us the money...

15:54.220 --> 15:56.021
They were supposed to
verify it with the bank,

15:56.022 --> 15:58.089
they didn't, and then we
should have verified it.

15:58.091 --> 16:00.091
So it kind of is our
mistake but since it's

16:00.093 --> 16:01.726
a transfer of a good
amount of money

16:01.728 --> 16:03.695
the bank shouldn't have
any problems with it.

16:03.697 --> 16:05.663
And I could go down there
with you if you'd like.

16:05.665 --> 16:06.731
No, I'm good.

16:06.733 --> 16:08.399
Everybody makes mistakes.

16:08.401 --> 16:10.668
Don't reprimand the
people in accounting,

16:10.670 --> 16:12.537
okay? It's not a big deal.

16:12.539 --> 16:14.372
And I should go
down there anyways.

16:14.374 --> 16:18.242
So this is standard
practice now?

16:18.244 --> 16:19.610
It's becoming.

16:19.612 --> 16:23.514
So then send a memo
to everybody, Benny.

16:23.516 --> 16:25.750
Alright, will do.

16:25.752 --> 16:28.086
And tell everybody that
it's standard practice

16:28.088 --> 16:30.555
that they need to detail
any foreign transfers

16:30.557 --> 16:32.757
of their account. Okay?

16:32.759 --> 16:34.092
Okay.

16:34.094 --> 16:35.693
What do you got for me, Dave?

16:35.695 --> 16:37.662
Top of the list is charitable.

16:37.664 --> 16:40.064
The new Brooklyn
hospital fundraiser.

16:40.066 --> 16:41.699
We can opt in at three levels:

16:41.701 --> 16:43.401
Silver, gold, and platinum

16:43.403 --> 16:45.770
at $50,000 or
$100,000 or $250,000.

16:45.772 --> 16:47.505
Understanding how you roll and-

16:47.507 --> 16:49.640
what's the money for?

16:49.642 --> 16:52.710
Like, is it going
straight to charity?

16:52.712 --> 16:57.181
'Cause you know when we
give money to charities

16:57.183 --> 17:01.119
we want to make sure
80% or 90% goes directly

17:01.121 --> 17:03.221
not to the administration,

17:03.223 --> 17:05.490
you know, I want it
to go to the charity.

17:05.492 --> 17:07.025
Already taken
care of that for you.

17:07.027 --> 17:08.726
Buddy, you do a great job.

17:08.728 --> 17:10.560
That's why you do that job.

17:10.563 --> 17:12.296
I just want to make sure.

17:12.298 --> 17:13.698
So what's this for?

17:13.700 --> 17:16.334
This is brand new care
units for the hospital.

17:16.336 --> 17:18.669
We have new equipment
coming in, um,

17:18.671 --> 17:21.105
all with your approval
from our meeting

17:21.107 --> 17:22.707
about six months ago.

17:22.709 --> 17:25.443
Okay, do it. Is
there anything else?

17:25.444 --> 17:27.211
No, understanding
how you roll, I know

17:27.213 --> 17:28.780
this is important
to you, I've already

17:28.782 --> 17:30.648
begun the paperwork
on the platinum level,

17:30.650 --> 17:32.316
with your permission of course.

17:32.318 --> 17:34.819
